1. *Stan* je bio mali, ali srećan. (The apartment was small, but happy.)
2. Ona je kupila novi *stan*. (She bought a new apartment.)
3. Ona je preselila u novi *stan*. (She moved to a new apartment.)
4. On je našao svoj *stan*. (He found his apartment.)
5. Ona je pronašla odgovarajući *stan*. (She found a suitable apartment.)
6. Oni su se preselili u veći *stan*. (They moved to a bigger apartment.)